OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 3 Jul to Sun 12 Jul
OL,6,FSome rain is possible across Scotland
OL,7,Fon Friday, easing as it spreads south
OL,8,Fand east before clearing away. High
OL,9,Fpressure will dominate across England
OL,10,Fand Wales over the weekend, bringing
OL,11,Fdry and warm conditions with plenty of
OL,12,Fsunshine for most. Scotland and
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland will probably see
OL,14,Fmore cloud this weekend, with periods
OL,15,Fof rain mainly affecting western
OL,16,FScotland at times. Into the following
OL,17,Fworking week, high pressure remains
OL,18,Fslow moving over England and Wales,
OL,19,Fperhaps extending northwards to bring
OL,20,Fdrier and warmer weather to Scotland
OL,21,Fand Northern Ireland. Winds will be
OL,22,Flight to moderate for most, though
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fstronger around northern hills and
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fcoasts near low pressure systems.
OL,25,FTemperatures will rise through the
OL,26,Fperiod, perhaps becoming very warm or
